node.title: Siege ends after masked gunman taken into custody on NSW south coast
node.description: A siege situation is resolved in a NSW south coast town near the Illawarra, after a masked man was seen firing shots outside a store.
node.content:
["A siege in the NSW south coast town of Windang, where a masked gunman was seen discharging shots in the main street, has ended.", "NSW Police confirmed a man was in custody after a brief stand-off with the gunmen outside a liquor store on Acacia Street.\u00a0", "Video shows a masked man, clad almost entirely in black, walking along the main strip of the Illawarra town firing a\u00a0shot\u00a0into the air.", "As the man walks past the main shops and a medical centre on Windang Road, which runs through the centre of town, a second weapon can seen slung around his shoulder.", "After circling parked cars and crossing the road, the man is seen collecting what appears to be a silver briefcase from the middle of the street.", "It is unclear how or why the case was left there.", "\"What the f*** is going on? Is he for f***ing real?\" a woman can be heard saying in footage posted on social media.", "Aerial footage then showed police with their firearms drawn, pressed up against the wall of a fishing store located next to a BWS, shortly after.", "", "
Police arrest gunman after multiple shots fired in Windang, NSW.(Facebook: Supplied)
", "Deputy Commissioner Mal Lanyon said the man had fired up to five shots.", "\"That male then subsequently went into a dollar shop premises in Windang at which stage further police and tactical police were called,\" he said.", "\"There were negotiations with the male while he was in that shop. He has subsequently surrendered and is in the custody of police and is under arrest at the moment.\"", "Footage on social media shows the man, now unmasked, being escorted out of the store by several police officers.", "Deputy Commissioner Lanyon said no-one was injured and there was no ongoing threat to the community.\u00a0", "He said it was \"still very early\" in the investigation and there was no clear motive for the man's actions.", "Traffic was stopped on Windang Bridge and roads around the town were closed.", "Police are expected to provide further information later today."]
